***********************************************************
BrickPi Python Code

This repository contains drivers and examples for using the BrickPi in Python.

DRIVERS:  This folder contains BrickPi.py, which you should include in your python program using the BrickPi.

Sensor Examples: Before starting with the examples, please copy "BrickPi.py" into the examples folder.


More information on BrickPi and Python is found on our website, here:  http://www.dexterindustries.com/BrickPi/program-it/python/

BrickPi is a Raspberry Pi Board that connects LEGO MINDSTORMS motors and sensors to the Raspberry Pi.

More information on hardware, firmware, and software can be found here:  http://www.dexterindustries.com/BrickPi

